  expeditionId: vine-cathedral
  orderIndex: 12
  chapterIndex: 2
  chapterTitle: Moonlit Ruins
  displayTitle: Vine Cathedral
  theme: 1
  openingStory: Ancient vines hang through the ruins like chandeliers. The shiny
    gem glows beyond them, apparently impressed by dramatic entrances.
  successStory: Four deliberate releases ring through the ruins. The vines are still
    swaying and may be applauding.
  lessonText: Hold through the arc. Release while rising forward for the strongest
    launch.
  failureHintText: Hold for another cycle if the vine is moving left. Release only
    on the forward rise.
